     title=""><a target="_blank" class="hover"
               title=""
               href="http://tymkrs.tumblr.com/post/3346218717/i-dun-wanna-learn-about-reactance-and-impedance"><div class="hover_inner"><span class="post_date">Feb 17, 2011</span><span class="post_notes"
